description: Scattered pavilions and tents dot the sunlit grassy area under the protective eye of a pair of guards stationed at the base of the tall southern wall.  Many well-used paths have been worn into the landscape by the merchants and travelers traversing the grassy sward.

title: [Guardian Keep, Outer Wall]
